=Description=

"It aims to put cities forward as drivers
of quality jobs and sustainable growth, as inclusive, diverse and creative; as green
and healthy, as smarter and innovative. To do so, it offers platforms for sharing
knowledge and exchanging ideas (e.g. thematic forums, working groups, projects,
activities, events) in domains like culture, economy, environment and mobility. Today, Eurocities brings together the local governments of over 140 of Europe’s largest cities and over 45 partner cities."

